summary: I cannot fucking believe the plot twist that has been sony’s redemption arc this year, Venom was like ‘Sony: first redemption’...
body: I cannot fucking believe the plot twist that has been sony’s redemption arc this year, Venom was like ‘Sony: first redemption’ and it was nice and I was already happy with it but they didn’t stop there and now we have Into the Spider-Verse which is basically ‘Sony: the days of future redemption’ and it’s like?? perfect ??? and I hope to god they don’t fuck it up on the third try and release ‘Sony: redemption apocalypse’ ! I hope to god they don’t do this ! @Sony I’m on your side now don’t fuck this up !!!

summary: I spent the greater chunk of yesterday playing Gravity Rush, after which we went to go see Spiderverse in theaters, and those...
body:
I spent the greater chunk of yesterday playing Gravity Rush, after which we went to go see Spiderverse in theaters, and those two things back to back had a pretty significant effect on me.

namely, I have a very rabid and completely unattainable desire to SWING WILDLY FROM TALL OBJECTS and SOAR WITHOUT A CARE THROUGH THE SKY, @ GOD IF WE’RE THE APEX PREDATOR WHAT’S WITH THESE CHAINS WE CALL GRAVITY HOLDING US BACK YOU DUMB ASSHOLE
